a.n: Fedde Le Grand - Grand, a new level in Dance

p.d: Grand At Ziggodome 2016 (60 minutes) Following is sold out shows in 2015 top DJ Fedde Le Grand decided to make a comeback in an bigger and more spectacular environment! Now turning to the Ziggo Dome for the biggest Grand edition to date. With the goal being simple: Taking down the barriers and breaking all codes of a traditional dance party, Grand is definitely set to be an astonishing show!
